<h2 class="sidebar">Categories</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.notesfrommadrid.com/category/madrid-how-tos/" title="View all posts filed under How To&#039;s / Where To&#039;s">How To&#8217;s / Where To&#8217;s</a>
</li>
<li><a href="http://www.notesfrommadrid.com/category/weird-quirky-fun/" title="View all posts filed under Weird : Quirky : Fun">Weird : Quirky : Fun</a>
</li>
	<li><a href="http://www.notesfrommadrid.com/category/travel-tips/" title="View all posts filed under Travel tips">Travel tips</a>
</li>
	<li><a href="http://www.notesfrommadrid.com/category/bars/" title="View all posts filed under Bars and Cafes">Bars and Cafes</a>
